      "eval_at_point R as p = eval_at_point R a (total_eval (Pring R {..<n}) (\<lambda>i. R.indexed_const x) (pre_to_univ_poly (Suc n) i p))"
    show "eval_at_point R as (p \<otimes>\<^bsub>Pring R {..<Suc n}\<^esub> pvar R j) =
